item.title: CVE-2018-1211|2024-08-05T03:51:48.979Z -- dell%20emc -- idrac7%2Fidrac8
item.description: Dell EMC iDRAC7/iDRAC8, versions prior to 2.52.52.52, contain a path traversal vulnerability in its Web server's URI parser which could be used to obtain specific sensitive data without authentication. A remote unauthenticated attacker may be able to read configuration settings from the iDRAC by querying specific URI strings.
